author: Michaelangelo Conte | The Jersey Journal
title: Jersey City woman charged with stabbing man in neck with umbrella after alleged burglary incident
text: A Jersey City woman charged with burglary, theft and extortion Saturday in a Hoboken incident was already under indictment in an attack in which a man was stabbed in the neck with an umbrella in Jersey City.
